label: Newton Plantation Stock keepers and Watchmen Book 1862
description: This book contains records of the wages and rents for stock keepers and watchmen for the year 1862.  It includes the amount of land rented, the rent for  the amount of land rented, the wages for the period, the deductions of rent from the wages, the amount paid after deductions and any arrears that may be outstanding at that point.  This book along with another section (book) detailing  Money Renters for  1892 are both included in one physical book.  The physical book is arranged in such a way that each section begins with a front cover.
